```

== Remarks ==
In some cases (e.g. OpenGL) and on some platforms (e.g. Microsoft Windows) the hint [[SDL_HINT_VIDEO_WINDOW_SHARE_PIXEL_FORMAT]] needs to be configured before using SDL_CreateWindowFrom().

